
<h2 id="home-notice" <%= 'class="error"' if flash[:error]%>>
	<%= flash[:error] || flash[:notice] %></h2>

<div id="home-content">

  <div id=left-sidebar>

    
    <div id=info-box1 class=right-info-box>

      <% if logged_in? and current_user.is_an_admin? %>
        <h3>Admin Tools</h3>
        <p><%= link_to "Parts Bin", bio_bytes_path if logged_in? and current_user.can_create_bio_bytes? %></p>
        <p><%= link_to "Protocol Generator", step_generators_path if logged_in? and current_user.can_edit_step_generators? %></p>
      <% end %>

    </div>

    <div id=info-box2 class=right-info-box>
      <h3>I am info box 2</h3>
      <p><i>Put a picture here or something, I'm so lonely...</i></p>
      
    </div>

  </div>

  <div id=center-content>

    <div id=main-info-box>

      <h2>YO WHATS THE DEAL DAWG:</h2>
      
      <p>
        <i>Genomikon: an Educational Toolkit for the Rapid Assembly of Plasmids</i>
      </p>

      <p>
        With Genomikon, you can make bacteria do all kinds of crazy crap! Like, glow in the dark
        or smell nice or whatever. The sky is the rainbow limit! Science is all sunshine and 
        fluffy clouds and bunnies that hop through the meadows.
      </p>

      <p>
        All you need to do is squirt some water into some tubes and drag magnets around or 
        something and then all your wildest dreams will come true!
      </p>

      <p><%= link_to "Learn more about this product", about_path %></p>

    </div>

    <div id=info-box3 class=center-info-box>
      <h3>Try it out!</h3>
      <p>Get started building your first plasmid right away, with our easy to use drag-and-drop plasmid constructor!</p>
      <p><%= link_to "click here for more...", sandbox_path %></p>
      
    </div>

    <div id=info-box4 class=center-info-box>
      
      <h3>Get the background!</h3>
       <p>Want to learn more about molecular biology? Check out our 
         <%= link_to "encyclopedia articles" , encyclopaedias_path %>
          and learn the science behind what goes on in the cells.
       </p>

      <h3>Brush up on your vocabulary</h3>
       <p>Forget what ligase is? Our 
         <%= link_to "glossary of terms",  glossaries_path %> 
         can help!
       </p>

    </div>

  </div>

  <div id=right-sidebar>
    <div id=info-box1 class=right-info-box>

      <h3>Get started</h3>
      <p><%= link_to "Login" , login_path %> or <%= link_to "sign up now" , signup_path %>
            to get started performing your very own molecular biology experiments!
      </p>

    </div>
    
    <div id=info-box2 class=right-info-box>

      <h3>See also:</h3>
      <p>
        Check out our team's <a href=http://2010.igem.org/Team:Alberta>project page</a>!
      </p>
      <p>
        Read comics about <a href=http://poo.ca>dinosaurs!</a>
      </p>
      
    </div>
  </div>

</div>
